  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This is a battle system using the mechanism of a card game, and is performed not by a digital monster card game but by rules peculiar to the game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The stage is a digital world where the intensity is determined by cards.\nIt is governed by seven card readers who are at the top of the card battle.\nBut File Island is threatened by a sudden bug card.\nThe card readers kept each other in check and wouldn't cooperate.\nThe hero summoned by Babamon is said to be a legendary hero. Babamon entrusted him with the deck and he collected Sevens cards.",
